e Seine River.\", \"from\": 1602, \"to\": 1773, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The performance\", \"from\": 1602, \"to\": 1617}, {\"ngram\": \"the controversy\", \"from\": 1631, \"to\": 1646}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 1652, \"to\": 1657}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening\", \"from\": 1661, \"to\": 1672}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 1676, \"to\": 1694}, {\"ngram\": \"the picturesque backdrop\", \"from\": 1708, \"to\": 1732}, {\"ngram\": \"the Eiffel Tower\", \"from\": 1736, \"to\": 1752}, {\"ngram\": \"the Seine River\", \"from\": 1757, \"to\": 1772}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The segment began with three French drag queens and other elaborately dressed dancers presenting what appeared to be a parody of \\\"The Last Supper.\\\"\", \"from\": 1774, \"to\": 1921, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1803, \"end\": 1809, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9999826778771052, \"rank\": 1.280583031878862e-05, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The segment\", \"from\": 1774, \"to\": 1785}, {\"ngram\": \"other elaborately dressed dancers\", \"from\": 1826, \"to\": 1859}, {\"ngram\": \"a parody\", \"from\": 1891, \"to\": 1899}, {\"ngram\": \"The Last Supper\", \"from\": 1904, \"to\": 1919}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The centerpiece of this act was a bedazzled woman adorned with a large silver headdress resembling a halo, which seemed to mock traditional depictions of Jesus.\", \"from\": 1923, \"to\": 2083, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2077, \"end\": 2082, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.9999999997248779, \"rank\": 2.7515456293182724e-10, \"text\": \"Jesus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The centerpiece\", \"from\": 1923, \"to\": 1938}, {\"ngram\": \"this act\", \"from\": 1942, \"to\": 1950}, {\"ngram\": \"a bedazzled woman\", \"from\": 1955, \"to\": 1972}, {\"ngram\": \"a large silver headdress\", \"from\": 1986, \"to\": 2010}, {\"ngram\": \"a halo\", \"from\": 2022, \"to\": 2028}, {\"ngram\": \"traditional depictions\", \"from\": 2051, \"to\": 2073}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This figure made a heart shape with her hands, while her peers engaged in a choreographed dance routine.\", \"from\": 2084, \"to\": 2188, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This figure\", \"from\": 2084, \"to\": 2095}, {\"ngram\": \"a heart shape\", \"from\": 2101, \"to\": 2114}, {\"ngram\": \"her hands\", \"from\": 2120, \"to\": 2129}, {\"ngram\": \"her peers\", \"from\": 2137, \"to\": 2146}, {\"ngram\": \"a choreographed dance routine\", \"from\": 2158, \"to\": 2187}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Following the uproar, Thomas Jolly, the artistic director of the opening ceremony, defended the production during a press conference on Sunday.\", \"from\": 2192, \"to\": 2335, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2214, \"end\": 2220, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clarence_Thomas\", \"score\": 0.9999849973230452, \"rank\": 1.5002313795153048e-05, \"text\": \"Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clarence_Thomas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clarence_Thomas\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the uproar\", \"from\": 2202, \"to\": 2212}, {\"ngram\": \"the artistic director\", \"from\": 2228, \"to\": 2249}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 2253, \"to\": 2273}, {\"ngram\": \"the production\", \"from\": 2284, \"to\": 2298}, {\"ngram\": \"a press conference\", \"from\": 2306, \"to\": 2324}, {\"ngram\": \"Sunday\", \"from\": 2328, \"to\": 2334}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jolly explained that the intention behind the performance was to celebrate \\\"inclusion\\\" rather than to be provocative.\", \"from\": 2336, \"to\": 2453, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the intention\", \"from\": 2357, \"to\": 2370}, {\"ngram\": \"the performance\", \"from\": 2378, \"to\": 2393}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"inclusion\", \"from\": 2411, \"to\": 2421}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Our subject was not to be subversive.\", \"from\": 2454, \"to\": 2492, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Our subject\", \"from\": 2455, \"to\": 2466}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We never wanted to be subversive.\", \"from\": 2493, \"to\": 2526, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We wanted to talk about diversity.\", \"from\": 2527, \"to\": 2561, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"diversity\", \"from\": 2551, \"to\": 2560}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Diversity means being together,\\\" Jolly said.\", \"from\": 2562, \"to\": 2606, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Diversity\", \"from\": 2562, \"to\": 2571}, {\"ngram\": \"Jolly\", \"from\": 2595, \"to\": 2600}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We wanted to include everyone, as simple as that.\", \"from\": 2608, \"to\": 2658, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 2630, \"to\": 2638}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In France, we have freedom of creation, artistic freedom.\", \"from\": 2659, \"to\": 2716, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2662, \"end\": 2668, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.8117330370075122, \"rank\": 0.21298458129732642, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"freedom\", \"from\": 2678, \"to\": 2685}, {\"ngram\": \"creation\", \"from\": 2689, \"to\": 2697}, {\"ngram\": \"artistic freedom\", \"from\": 2699, \"to\": 2715}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are lucky in France to live in a free country.\", \"from\": 2717, \"to\": 2766, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2733, \"end\": 2739, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.8117330370075122, \"rank\": 0.21298458129732642, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a free country\", \"from\": 2751, \"to\": 2765}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I did not have any specific messages that I wanted to deliver.\", \"from\": 2767, \"to\": 2829, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any specific messages\", \"from\": 2782, \"to\": 2803}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In France, we are republic, we have the right to love whom we want, we have the right not to be worshippers, we have a lot of rights in France, and this is what I wanted to convey,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 2830, \"to\": 3021, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2833, \"end\": 2839, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.8117330370075122, \"rank\": 0.21298458129732642, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 2966, \"end\": 2972, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.8117330370075122, \"rank\": 0.21298458129732642, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the right\", \"from\": 2866, \"to\": 2875}, {\"ngram\": \"the right\", \"from\": 2906, \"to\": 2915}, {\"ngram\": \"worshippers\", \"from\": 2926, \"to\": 2937}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 2947, \"to\": 2952}, {\"ngram\": \"rights\", \"from\": 2956, \"to\": 2962}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jolly further clarified his intentions in a conversation with The Associated Press.\", \"from\": 3023, \"to\": 3106, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3089, \"end\": 3105, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\", \"score\": 0.9994818397026376, \"rank\": 0.0005184289266062126, \"text\": \"Associated Press\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his intentions\", \"from\": 3047, \"to\": 3061}, {\"ngram\": \"a conversation\", \"from\": 3065, \"to\": 3079}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My wish is not to be subversive, nor to mock or to shock,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 3107, \"to\": 3175, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My wish\", \"from\": 3108, \"to\": 3115}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Most of all, I wanted to send a message of love, a message of inclusion and not at all to divide.\\\"\", \"from\": 3176, \"to\": 3275, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a message\", \"from\": 3207, \"to\": 3216}, {\"ngram\": \"love\", \"from\": 3220, \"to\": 3224}, {\"ngram\": \"a message\", \"from\": 3226, \"to\": 3235}, {\"ngram\": \"inclusion\", \"from\": 3239, \"to\": 3248}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite Jolly's explanation, the performancedrew sharp criticism from various quarters, particularly from religious conservatives.\", \"from\": 3279, \"to\": 3409, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Jolly's explanation\", \"from\": 3287, \"to\": 3306}, {\"ngram\": \"various quarters\", \"from\": 3349, \"to\": 3365}, {\"ngram\": \"religious conservatives\", \"from\": 3385, \"to\": 3408}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Marion Marechal, a practicing Catholic, took to X to express her disapproval: \\\"To all the Christians of the world who are watching the #Paris2024 ceremony and felt insulted by this drag queen parody of the Last Supper, know that it is not France that is speaking but a left-wing minority ready for any provocation.\\\"\", \"from\": 3411, \"to\": 3726, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3441, \"end\": 3449, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"score\": 0.9999998415492098, \"rank\": 1.5844217705903054e-07, \"text\": \"C